queries.sql: SELECT c.descripcion, SUM(vd.cantidad) AS total_vendidos, p.imagen FROM ventas_detalle vd JOIN productos p ON p.id_producto = vd.producto_id JOIN categoria c ON c.id_categoria = p.categoria_id WHERE c.activo = 1 GROUP BY c.id_categoria ORDER BY total_vendidos DESC LIMIT 3

timelineData.name: Query
timelineData.query: SELECT c.descripcion, SUM(vd.cantidad) AS total_vendidos, p.imagen FROM ventas_detalle vd JOIN productos p ON p.id_producto = vd.producto_id JOIN categoria c ON c.id_categoria = p.categoria_id WHERE c.activo = 1 GROUP BY c.id_categoria ORDER BY total_vendidos DESC LIMIT 3
